-- Turkey Gives Out Bosporus Bridge Tender Documents, Sabah Says
-- B y   B e n j a m i n   H a r v e y
-- 2012-04-19T05:39:42Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-19/turkey-gives-out-bosporus-bridge-tender-documents-sabah-says.html
Turkey gave tender documents to 11
companies that may bid to build a third bridge over the Bosporus
in Istanbul,  Sabah newspaper  reported.  The companies are Turkey’s Alsim Alarko, Park Holding,
Cengiz Insaat, Atli Makina, Mapa Insaat, STFA Insaat, Guris
Insaat and Yapi Merkezi;  Italy ’s Salini SpA and Astaldi; and
 Posco (005490)  E&C of  South Korea , the newspaper said, adding that the
tender will be held tomorrow.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Benjamin Harvey in Istanbul at 
 bharvey11@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gavin Serkin at 
 gserkin@bloomberg.net  